data.description: Unleash your senses in this extraordinary oasis! Step into a world of breathtaking beauty. Feast your eyes on this magnificent 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, where every inch has been meticulously crafted to provide an unparalleled living experience.Prepare to be captivated by the dazzling kitchen, adorned w/high-end finishes.The pantry is every chef's dream, offering ample space to keep your culinary treasures neatly organized & easily accessible. As you explore further, you'll discover a floor plan that seamlessly blends elegance w/functionality. The formal dining area beckons you to host in the joy of entertainment.The primary bedroom it?s a private sanctuary where serenity & opulence converge, creating a haven of tranquility that will leave you utterly enchanted. Step outside onto the enchanting, covered deck, where you'll find yourself surrounded by an exquisite garden bursting with vibrant blooms & luscious fruit trees. This outdoor paradise is fully fenced, ensuring your privacy while sitting around your fire pit or relaxing in your hot tub Imagine savoring the soothing warmth, surrounded by stars twinkling overhead or sharing laughter-filled evenings with loved ones, creating memories.Prepare to be awestruck by the impressive 36x36 shop that awaits you. Plus, AMPLE parking! This architectural marvel boasts not just one, but three spacious bays, each equipped with its own door. The 220-amp service ensures that your power needs are met, whether you're pursuing your hobbies,Working on projects, or storing your prized possessions.This show-stopping property is not just a house; it's a canvas upon which dreams come to life. It's an enchanting retreat where luxurious living meets the soul-soothing wonders of nature. Don't let this opportunity slip away - come and experience the sheer magnificence of this home for yourself. Prepare to be enchanted, prepare to be amazed, prepare to fall irrevocably in love. Claim your sanctuary & your haven!
